16 (C) (1) EACH HOSPITAL LICENSED UNDER THIS TITLE SHALL ESTABLISH
17 AND MAINTAIN A CLINICAL STAFFING COMMITTEE THAT HAS EQUAL MEMBERSHIP
18 FROM MANAGEMENT AND EMPLOYEES.
19 (2) EACH CLINICAL STAFFING COMMITTEE ESTABLISHED UNDER
20 THIS PART SHALL INCLUDE AT LEAST ONE OF THE FOLLOWING INDIVIDUALS:
21 (I) A CERTIFIED NURSING ASSISTANT;
22 (II) A DIETARY AIDE;
23 (III) AN EMERGENCY ROOM NURSE;
24 (IV) AN ENVIRONMENTAL SERVICE WORKER;
25 (V) 1. A RESIDENT, IF THE COMMITTEE IS IN A TEACHING
26 HOSPITAL; OR
27 2. A PHYSICIAN, IF THE COMMITTEE IS IN A HOSPITAL
28 THAT IS NOT A TEACHING HOSPITAL; AND

