9 SECTION 2. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That each hospital shall establish
10 a clinical staffing committee as required under § 19–388 of the Health – General Article,
11 as enacted by Section 1 of this Act, on or before January 1, 2026.
12 SECTION 3. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That each clinical staffing
13 committee shall develop a clinical staffing plan as required under § 19–388 of the
14 Health – General Article, as enacted by Section 1 of this Act, on or before July 1, 2026.
15 SECTION 4. AND BE IT FURTHER ENACTED, That this Act shall take effect
16 October 1, 2025.

